hMailServer Vacation plugin for SquirrelMail
========================================
Ver 2.0, 2007-01-12

Author: 		 Martin Knafve
modified by: Dr. Mario Roediger <info_hmailserver@mrxs.de> 

Description
===========

This plugin allows your users to set vacation/autoresponder
messages when you use the hMailServer mailserver. It is based
on the Courier vacation plugin written by Paul Lesneiwski.

It's necessary that you specify your main hMailServer password 
and some other settings in config.php.